      "text_block": {
        "title": "设伏",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f1_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "朱儁说：妖术怕脏东西。准备猪羊狗血，装在桶里，埋伏在山后高冈上。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f1_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "关羽带一千人在左面山冈，张飞带一千人在右面。蹲着，等着。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.002,
        "w": 1.0,
        "h": 0.2529
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f2",
      "scene_id": "cp002_p01_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp002-p01-page-01-f2",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "妖法再来",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f2_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "第二天，张宝又来了。旗帜招展，鼓声震天。刘备出阵接战，几个回合后拨马便走。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f2_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "张宝挥军追来，又作妖法——风雷大作，黑气从天压下，比昨天还猛。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.0,
        "y": 0.2549,
        "w": 0.5009,
        "h": 0.4634
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f3",
      "scene_id": "cp002_p01_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp002-p01-page-01-f3",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "破法",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f3_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "追兵过了山脚，冲上坡道——一声号炮。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f3_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "左右伏兵同时站起，秽物齐泼。黑气里的人影马影——纸做的，草扎的，纷纷坠地。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
      "panel_box": {
        "x": 0.5009,
        "y": 0.2549,
        "w": 0.4991,
        "h": 0.4634
      }
    },
    {
      "frame_id": "f4",
      "scene_id": "cp002_p01_s2",
      "image_slot": {
        "asset_key": "cp002-p01-page-01-f4",
        "aspect_ratio": "4:3",
        "crop_mode": "contain"
      },
      "text_block": {
        "title": "追杀",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "f4_t1",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "还没来得及后撤，左关羽、右张飞，两路杀到。背后主力也压上来了。三面夹击，黄巾军瞬间崩了。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          },
          {
            "id": "f4_t2",
            "kind": "caption",
            "speaker": "narrator",
            "text": "刘备看见\u201c地公将军\u201d旗号，飞马追去，一箭射中张宝左臂。张宝捂着胳膊跑进了阳城，关上城门，死不出来。",
            "lang": "zh-CN"
          }
        ]
      },
